    "121712633": {
      "title": "Outer generalized inverses in rings",
      "abstract": "ABSTRACT In this article we formulate basic results on outer generalized inverses of elements in rings. We characterize elements which have the same idempotents related to their particular outer generalized inverses and investigate positive generalized inverses in C*-algebras."
    },
    "15404005": {
      "title": "On the (p, q)-outer generalized inverse in Banach algebras",
      "abstract": "Abstract In this note, the ( p , q ) outer generalized inverse in Banach algebra is considered, a new representation based on the (1, 5) inverse is presented. Also, we construct an iterative method for computing the ( p , q ) outer generalized inverse in Banach algebra."
    },
